headline: From Waste Into Worth: How Trane Technologies' Tiffany Waymer Drives Circularity Through Scrap
summary: Where most people see waste, Tiffany Waymer sees materials with untapped value. As a materials engineer at Trane Technologies, she works inside real-world constraints to turn circular design into measurable climate impact. NORTHAMPTON, MA / ACCESS ...
